<body>

    <%- include('includes/navbar') %>

    <header class="bg-warning text-white text-center py-5">
        <h1>About BidBazar</h1>
    </header>

    <main class="container py-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>BIDBAZAR is selling property and products via a Web Based Electronic Auction. This
                    auction will be activated for a period of time clearly stating from this date and will end on
                    this date. During this period you can actively take part and submit your bid for the product.

                    Maximum number of bids on one item is stated at each item. During the auction you should monitor
                    your bids so you can react on all
                    bids price development.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2>IMPORTANT INFORMATION:</h2>
                <p>1. ALL ITEMS ARE BEING SOLD ON "AS IS AND WHERE IS" BASIS. <br>
                    2. NO WARRANTY AND GUARANTY OF ANY ITEMS. <br>
                    3. ITEMS ONCE SOLD WILL NOT BE RETURNED AND ARE NON-REFUNDABLE.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>How to pay for your items? <br>
                    The successful bidder shall deposit 100% payment in Cash within three days on
                    acceptance of the bid by the competent authority, if the bidder failed to pay the amount, the item
                    will be given to the second bidder. </p>
            </div>
         
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col">
                <h2>Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Transparency: We believe in maintaining a transparent platform where all auction details are
                        clearly communicated to both sellers and buyers.</li>
                    <li>Fairness: We ensure fairness by providing equal opportunities to all participants and
                        prohibiting any fraudulent or unethical activities.</li>
                    <li>Customer Satisfaction: We strive to deliver an exceptional user experience and provide prompt
                        support to address any concerns or issues.</li>
                    <li>Innovation: We continuously explore new features and technologies to enhance the bidding and
                        auction experience for our users.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('includes/footer') %>


